#: ../../doc/template_type.rst:2
msgid "Registering Template Types"
msgstr "注册模板类型"

#: ../../doc/template_type.rst:5
msgid "Constructors and Factories"
msgstr "构造函数与工厂函数"

#: ../../doc/template_type.rst:7
msgid ""
"For template types, AngelScript will pass a hidden ``asITypeInfo*`` in "
"the front of arguments, indicating an instantiation of the template. It "
"will be automatically handled by the library with the special binding "
"generators of templated types, which are named ``template_value_class`` "
"and ``template_ref_class``."
msgstr ""
"对于模板类型，AngelScript 会在参数前面传递一个隐藏的 ``asITypeInfo*`` 参数，"
"表示模板的一个实例化。库将使用模板类型的特殊绑定生成器"
"（即 ``template_value_class`` 和 ``template_ref_class``）自动处理此参数。"

#: ../../doc/template_type.rst:13
msgid ""
"``asGetTypeTraits<T>()`` cannot determine the type flags for a template "
"value type, because its constructors contain parameters of the hidden "
"``asITypeInfo*``."
msgstr ""
"``asGetTypeTraits<T>()`` 无法确定模板值类型的类型标志，"
"因为其构造函数包含隐藏的 ``asITypeInfo*`` 参数。"

#: ../../doc/template_type.rst:16
msgid ""
"As a result, you need to manually pass the flags to the binding "
"generator. This also applies to the ``.behaviours_by_traits()`` helper."
msgstr ""
"因此，您需要手动将标志传递给绑定生成器。"
"这也适用于 ``.behaviours_by_traits()`` 辅助函数。"

#: ../../doc/template_type.rst:19
msgid "Here are examples from the unit tests."
msgstr "以下是来自单元测试的示例。"

#: ../../doc/template_type.rst:48
msgid "Methods of a Template Class"
msgstr "模板类的方法"

#: ../../doc/template_type.rst:50
msgid ""
"Methods are registered the same way as ordinary types. You can directly "
"use the subtype in the declaration of method."
msgstr ""
"方法的注册方式与普通类型相同。"
"您可以直接在方法声明中使用子类型。"

#: ../../doc/template_type.rst:63
msgid ""
"If the subtype might be an object handle, you probably need to consider "
"the keyword ``if_handle_then_const``."
msgstr ""
"如果子类型可能是对象句柄，"
"您可能需要考虑使用 ``if_handle_then_const`` 关键字。"

#: ../../doc/template_type.rst:66
msgid ""
"You can also read `official document explaining this "
"<https://www.angelcode.com/angelscript/sdk/docs/manual/doc_adv_template.html#doc_adv_template_1_1>`_"
msgstr ""
"您也可以阅读 `解释此问题的官方文档 "
"<https://www.angelcode.com/angelscript/sdk/docs/manual/doc_adv_template.html#doc_adv_template_1_1>`_"

#: ../../doc/template_type.rst:75
msgid "Callback for Validating Template Instantiations"
msgstr "验证模板实例化的回调"

#: ../../doc/template_type.rst:77
msgid ""
"In order to avoid unnecessary runtime validations of invalid template "
"instantiations, the application should preferably register a validator by"
" ``.template_callback``. Its underlying type behaviour is "
"``asBEHAVE_TEMPLATE_CALLBACK``."
msgstr ""
"为了避免对无效模板实例化进行不必要的运行时验证，"
"应用程序最好通过 ``.template_callback`` 注册验证器。"
"其底层类型行为是 ``asBEHAVE_TEMPLATE_CALLBACK``。"

#: ../../doc/template_type.rst:81
msgid ""
"The callback function must be a global function that receives a pointer "
"to ``asITypeInfo*`` as its first parameter, and should return a boolean. "
"If the template instance is valid the return value should be ``true``."
msgstr ""
"回调函数必须是一个全局函数，接收一个指向 ``asITypeInfo*`` 的指针作为第一个参数，"
"并应返回一个布尔值。如果模板实例有效，返回值应为 ``true``。"

#: ../../doc/template_type.rst:85
msgid ""
"The function should also take a second parameter with an output reference"
" to a boolean. This parameter should be set to ``true`` by the function "
"if the template instance should not be garbage collected, which will make"
" AngelScript clear the ``asOBJ_GC`` flag for the object type. If the "
"template instance cannot form any circular references, then it doesn't "
"need to be garbage collected, which reduces the work that has to be done "
"by the garbage collector."
msgstr ""
"函数还应接受一个布尔值的输出引用作为第二个参数。"
"如果模板实例不应被垃圾回收，则该参数应由函数设置为 ``true``，"
"这将使 AngelScript 清除该对象类型的 ``asOBJ_GC`` 标志。"
"如果模板实例无法形成任何循环引用，则无需进行垃圾回收，"
"从而减少垃圾回收器的工作量。"

