#: ../../doc/template_type.rst:119
msgid "Template Specializations"
msgstr "模板特化"

#: ../../doc/template_type.rst:121
msgid ""
"When registering a template specialization, you override the template "
"instance that AngelScript would normally create when compiling a "
"declaration with the template type. This allow the application to "
"register a completely different object with its own implementation for "
"template specializations."
msgstr ""
"注册模板特化时，您覆盖了 AngelScript 在编译带有模板类型的声明时通常会创建的模板实例。"
"这允许应用程序为模板特化注册一个具有自己实现的完全不同的对象。"

#: ../../doc/template_type.rst:125
msgid ""
"Template specializations are registered like :doc:`ordinary types "
"<object_type>`, except the type name should be the instantiated name."
msgstr ""
"模板特化的注册方式与 :doc:`普通类型 <object_type>` 类似，"
"只是类型名称应为实例化后的名称。"

